<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="興福" xml:id="gsz0879b13shiHanGuang"><lb
ed="T" n="0879b13"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0879b13"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>京兆大興善寺<persName key="A000459">含光</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0879b14"/><persName key="A000459">釋含光</persName>，不知何許人也。幼覺囂塵，馳求簡<lb
ed="T" n="0879b15"/>靜。<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371992113" notAfter-iso="+0742-02-13">開元中</date>見<persName key="A000095">不空三藏</persName>頗高時望，乃依附<lb
ed="T" n="0879b16"/>焉。及<persName key="A000095">不空</persName><anchor xml:id="beg0879sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>劫</sic><corr>却</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0879sgsz3"/>迴<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName><persName key="A000459">光</persName>亦影隨，匪憚艱危，<lb
ed="T" n="0879b17"/>思尋聖迹。去時泛舶海中，遇巨魚望舟，有<lb
ed="T" n="0879b18"/>吞噬之意。兩遭黑風，天吳異物之怪，既從恬<lb
ed="T" n="0879b19"/>靜，俄抵<placeName key="PL000000048734">師子國</placeName>。屬<persName key="A013729">尊賢阿闍梨</persName>建大悲胎藏<lb
ed="T" n="0879b20"/>壇，許<persName key="A000459">光</persName>并<persName key="A008835">慧𧦬</persName>同受五部灌頂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g97"/>法。<date from-iso="+0747-02-18" key="j19939441994298" to-iso="+0748-02-07"><name>天寶</name>六<lb
ed="T" n="0879b21"/>載</date>迴<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>，<persName key="A000095">不空</persName>譯經，乃當參議華<name>梵</name>，屬<persName key="A000095">師</persName>卒。<lb
ed="T" n="0879b22"/>後<persName key="A004379">代宗</persName>重<persName key="A000459">光</persName>，如見<persName key="A000095">不空</persName>，勅委往<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺山</placeName>修<lb
ed="T" n="0879b23"/>功德。時天台宗學湛然解了禪觀，深得智<lb
ed="T" n="0879b24"/>者膏腴，甞與<placeName key="PL000000005250">江淮</placeName>僧四十餘人入<placeName key="PL000000005250">清涼</placeName>境<lb
ed="T" n="0879b25"/>界。<persName key="A001307">湛然</persName>與<persName key="A000459">光</persName>相見，問<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>傳法之事。<persName key="A000459">光</persName>云：<lb
ed="T" n="0879b26"/>「有一國僧體解空宗，問及<persName key="A001301">智者</persName>教法。<name>梵</name>僧<lb
ed="T" n="0879b27"/>云：『曾聞此教定邪正，曉偏圓，明止觀，功推<lb
ed="T" n="0879b28"/>第一。』再三囑<persName key="A000459">光</persName>或因緣重至，為<anchor xml:id="beg0879sgsz5"/>翻<anchor xml:id="end0879sgsz5"/>唐為<name>梵</name><lb
ed="T" n="0879b29"/>附來，某願受持。屢屢<anchor xml:id="beg0879001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>掘</sic><corr>握</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0879001"/>手叮囑。詳其<placeName key="PL000000048209">南印<pb ed="T" n="0879c" xml:id="T50.2061.0879c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0879c01"/>土</placeName>多行<persName key="A001482">龍樹</persName>宗見，故有此願流布也。」<persName key="A000459">光</persName>不<lb
ed="T" n="0879c02"/>知其終。</p>
    <p><lb
ed="T" n="0879c03"/>系曰：未聞<placeName key="PL000000000083">中華</placeName>演述佛教，倒傳<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>，有諸<lb
ed="T" n="0879c04"/>乎？通曰：「昔<date from-iso="+0502-05-02" key="j19045331921743" to-iso="+0549-06-14">梁武世</date>，<placeName key="PL000000047059">吐谷渾</placeName><persName key="A019484">夸呂可汗</persName>使來求<lb
ed="T" n="0879c05"/>佛像及經論十四條，<persName key="A002098">帝</persName>與所撰涅槃、<anchor xml:id="beg0879002"/>般<anchor xml:id="end0879002"/>若、金<lb
ed="T" n="0879c06"/>光明等經疏一百三卷付之。原其使者必通<lb
ed="T" n="0879c07"/><name>華</name>言，既達音字，到後以彼土言譯華成胡，<lb
ed="T" n="0879c08"/>方令通會。彼亦有僧，必展轉傳譯，從<placeName key="PL000000047059">青海</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0879c09"/>西達<placeName key="PL000000049639">葱嶺</placeName>北諸國，不久均行<placeName key="PL000000048207">五竺</placeName>，更無疑<lb
ed="T" n="0879c10"/>矣。故<placeName key="PL000000047462">車師</placeName>有毛詩、論語、孝經，置學官弟子，<lb
ed="T" n="0879c11"/>以相教授。雖習讀之，皆為胡語是也。又唐<lb
ed="T" n="0879c12"/><placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>求易、道經，詔僧道譯唐為<name>梵</name>。二教<lb
ed="T" n="0879c13"/>爭菩提為道，紛拏不已，中輟。設能翻傳到<lb
ed="T" n="0879c14"/>彼，見此方玄賾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g331"/>之典籍，豈不美歟！又夫<placeName key="PL000000055436">西<lb
ed="T" n="0879c15"/>域</placeName>者，佛法之根<anchor xml:id="beg0879sgsz7"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>[榦-木+禾]</sic><corr>幹</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0879sgsz7"/>也。<placeName key="PL000000000083">東夏</placeName>者，傳來之枝葉也。<lb
ed="T" n="0879c16"/>世所知者，知枝葉不知根<anchor xml:id="beg0879sgsz9"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>[榦-木+禾]</sic><corr>幹</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0879sgsz9"/>。而不知<anchor xml:id="begd1e47023"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>技</sic><corr>枝</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="endd1e47023"/>葉<lb
ed="T" n="0879c17"/>殖土，亦根生<anchor xml:id="beg0879sgsz11"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>[榦-木+禾]</sic><corr>幹</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0879sgsz11"/>長矣，尼拘律陀樹是也。蓋東<lb
ed="T" n="0879c18"/>人之敏利，何以知耶？秦人好略，驗其言少而<lb
ed="T" n="0879c19"/>解多也。<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>之人淳朴，何以知乎？<placeName key="PL000000048207">天竺</placeName>好<lb
ed="T" n="0879c20"/>繁，證其言重而後悟也。由是觀之，<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0879c21"/>人利在乎念性，東人利在乎解性也。如無<lb
ed="T" n="0879c22"/>相空教，出乎<persName key="A001482">龍樹</persName>，<persName key="A001301">智者</persName>演之，令<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>之仰<lb
ed="T" n="0879c23"/>慕。如中道教生乎<persName key="A001428">彌勒</persName>，<persName key="A001019">慈恩</persName>解之，疑<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0879c24"/>之罕及。將知以前二宗，殖於<persName key="A001301">智者</persName>、<persName key="A001019">慈恩</persName>之土<lb
ed="T" n="0879c25"/>中，枝葉也。入土別生根<anchor xml:id="beg0879sgsz13"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>[榦-木+禾]</sic><corr>幹</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0879sgsz13"/>，明矣。善<anchor xml:id="beg0879003"/>栽<anchor xml:id="end0879003"/>接者，<lb
ed="T" n="0879c26"/>見而不識，聞而可愛也。又如合浦之珠，北<lb
ed="T" n="0879c27"/>土之人得之，結步搖而飾冠珮。<placeName key="PL000000030463">南海</placeName>之人<lb
ed="T" n="0879c28"/>見而不識，聞而可愛也。蠶婦之絲，巧匠之<lb
ed="T" n="0879c29"/>家得之，繡衣裳而成黼黻。縿抽之嫗，見而<pb ed="T" n="0880a" xml:id="T50.2061.0880a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0880a01"/>不識，聞而可愛也。懿乎<persName key="A001301">智者</persName>、<persName key="A001019">慈恩</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0880a02"/>師<anchor xml:id="beg0880001"/>焉<anchor xml:id="end0880001"/>得不宗仰乎！」</p>
